{"word":"Concubinage","slug":"concubinage","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Concubinage</b> Laws concerning:<br/> - General references<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=21&verse=11'>Exo 21:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=19&verse=22'>Lev 19:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=21&verse=14'>Deu 21:14</a> <br/> - Concubines might be dismissed<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=21&verse=14'>Gen 21:14</a> <br/> - Called Wives<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=37&verse=2'>Gen 37:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=19&verse=5'>Jdg 19:5</a> <br/> - Children of, not heirs<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=15&verse=4'>Gen 15:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=21&verse=10'>Gen 21:10</a> <br/> Practiced by:<br/> - Abraham<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=16&verse=3'>Gen 16:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=25&verse=6'>Gen 25:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=1&verse=32'>1Ch 1:32</a> <br/> - Nahor<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=22&verse=24'>Gen 22:24</a> <br/> - Jacob<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=30&verse=4'>Gen 30:4</a> <br/> - Eliphaz<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=36&verse=12'>Gen 36:12</a> <br/> - Gideon<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=8&verse=31'>Jdg 8:31</a> <br/> - A Levite<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=19&verse=1'>Jdg 19:1</a> <br/> - Caleb<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=2&verse=48'>1Ch 2:48</a> <br/> - Manasseh<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=7&verse=14'>1Ch 7:14</a> <br/> - Saul<br/> <a href='https://www.wordo